<div class="modal-dialog modal-sm">
  <div class="modal-content">
    <div class="modal-header">
      <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">&times;</button>
      <div class="modal-title" id="myModalLabel">Quick Start Instructions</div>
    </div>
    <div class="lightbox-popup-content">
      <ol>
        <li>
          Answer each of the 50 questions in the diagnostic. It takes about an hour.
          </br>
          <ol>
            <li>
              For each dimension, rate your current level of maturity and the importance of each item from (1-5)
            </li>
            <li>
              Choose <i>‘Add to Plan’, ‘In Your Plan’</i> or <i>'Not Applicable'</i>.
            </li>
          </ol>
        </li>
        <li>
          If added to your plan, prioritize the dimension: (Must, Should, Could)
        </li>
        <li>
          Press <i>'Confirm'</i> to register your response.
        </li>
        <!-- <li>
          4. You can optionally add items  to your plan. If you add an item to the pla, you can enter a priority (must, should, could).
        </li>
        <li>
          5. Press 'Confirm' to register your response. You can return to edit items.
        </li> -->
      </ol>
      <p>If you have any questions or need help, contact us at <%= mail_to 'contact@revenuearchitects.com' %></p>
      </br>
      <%= check_box_tag "prevent_popup", id: "prevent_popup" %>
      <span class="checkbox-popup-label">
        <%= "Don't show this on next visit."%>
      <span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
